title: Newark Valley rebounds with key win at Sidney
text:
Newark Valley rebounds with key win at Sidney 
By wbng sports October 17, 2015 Updated Oct 17, 2015 at 12:12 AM EDT 
Sidney, NY (WBNG Binghamton) Newark Valley rebounded from its first loss of the season by winning a key divisional game at Sidney, 35-18. 
With the win, the Cardinals locked up a playoff spot in Class C. With a 2-1 division record, Newark Valley can finish with a loss to Whitney Point in Week 8 and still make the playoffs -- the Cardinals own head-to-head tiebreakers over Greene and Sidney.
